{"tid":2358531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"九把刀《月老》首支預告","createTime":"2021-01-08T08:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T12:55:11.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b0cd6085262a26403a88d1a7ba8203fedd5918","tid":2358531,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3gmRGIQHTYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3gmRGIQHTYw&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ad24fda6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3gmRGIQHTYw</a><br />\n<br />\n九把刀執導的電影《月老》預計將於今年上映，他自嘲：「劈腿被抓包後一直被全世界糗到炸裂的我，還可以拍愛情電影嗎？」還說《月老》的經典台詞又是「有些事，一萬年也不會變」，大方自挖舊事。<br />\n<br />\n電影改編自他的著作，究竟製作方為何要找他來拍愛情電影，九把刀並沒有真正詢問過，認為電影的起點是劇本，自己寫的小說由自己改寫成劇本還是非常有把握，他從2019年初開始寫劇本，一直到2019年底才開拍。提到電影台詞，他也沒忘自己曾經轟動一時的劈腿事件，「劈腿被抓包後一直被全世界糗到炸裂的我，還可以拍愛情電影嗎？而且《月老》的經典台詞又是『有些事，一萬年也不會變』，幹幹幹幹幹幹台詞這麼硬！超硬！哇靠真的太衝擊了！太需要恥力了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夠無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c363821e86666b63370a66a15926cb7f7d59c0","tid":2358531,"uid":49424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"個預告同想像有啲出入咁，希望到時成品好地地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a381ae542b8f0d86f46b1e678e521d9bcaac93cd","tid":2358531,"uid":13381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"覺得啲cg同上一套一樣柒柒地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但月老希望整得好好睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6189ec021021396ef3a1bcfa168d2360a6ab68","tid":2358531,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"又係柯震東同宋芸樺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有返校條女王淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2